videos.headline: LSU holds off Florida in high-scoring affair
videos.description: Max Johnson throws three touchdown passes and Tyrion Davis-Price rushes for another three TDs to hold off No. 20 Florida 49-42.

videos.headline: Davis-Price carries LSU past No. 20 UF with record day
videos.description: In the highest-scoring game in LSU-UF history, Tigers RB Tyrion Davis-Price amasses three TDs and a school record 287 rushing yards to top the Gators, 49-42.

videos.headline: LSU's Davis-Price: 'I'm ready to go another game'
videos.description: After rushing for a school record 287 yards and three TDs on 36 carries, LSU's Tyrion Davis-Price declares he's ready to go four more quarters.
